The paper deals with the problem of learning optimization algorithms for training neural nets, which is a core problem in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves experiments on image datasets, which suggests that it could belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the proposed method involves reinforcement learning, which could make it relevant to cs.SY (Systems and Control).
